'''热带风暴达尼埃尔'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Danielle}}）是[[1986年大西洋飓风季|1986年大西洋飓风季]]中唯一经过[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]的[[热带气旋|热带风暴]]。系统的持续时间较短，于9月7日在[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]南部以东发展形成，之后逐渐增强，达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]95公里的最高强度后经过[[圣文森特和格林纳丁斯|圣文森特和格林纳丁斯]]，[[雨带|雨带]]从[[圣文森特岛|圣文森特岛]]上空掠过并产生接近飓风强度阵风。气旋继续西进，最终在吸收[[南美洲|南美洲]]北部的干燥空气后于9月10日消散。

面对风暴威胁，[[巴巴多斯|巴巴多斯]]、圣文森特和格林纳丁斯发布烈风警告，巴巴多斯测得时速64公里的阵风。大风在圣文森特岛引发大面积停电，农作物也因暴雨受损。气旋过去数周后，又有另一个天气系统在该国产生降水，同达尼埃尔一起造成价值930万美元（1986年[[美元|美元]]）的破坏。风暴造成部分民居被毁，142人只能暂时住进避难所，共有436套住宅受到一定程度影响。气旋的外围雨带在[[千里达及托巴哥|千里达及托巴哥]]引发洪灾和[[泥石流|泥石流]]。更偏西面的[[牙买加|牙买加]]也一度受到达尼埃尔威胁，但风暴在袭击该岛前便已消散。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Danielle 1986 track.png}}
9月1日左右，有[[东风波|东风波]]离开[[非洲|非洲]]西海岸进入[[大西洋|大西洋]]。系统以中等速度在热带大西洋上空逐渐西进，再于9月6日加速至每小时37公里。9月7日清晨，东风波沿线发展出热带低气压，气象机构根据卫星图像估计气旋很快就在小安的列斯群岛的[[格林纳达|格林纳达]]东南偏东方向约620公里海域增强成热带风暴，于是以“达尼埃尔”（{{lang|en|Danielle}}）为其命名。<ref name="prelim">{{cite report | author = Gilbert B. Clark | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | work = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | year = 1986 | title = Tropical Storm Danielle Preliminary Report | accessdate = 2016-05-22 | format = [[GIF|GIF]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303184215/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1986-prelim/danielle/prelim01.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1986-prelim/danielle/prelim01.gif | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | location = [[迈阿密|Miami]], [[佛罗里达州|FL]] | date =  }}</ref><ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-021716.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-02-17 | accessdate = 2016-05-22 | archivedate = 2016-04-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160411090349/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-021716.txt | deadurl = no | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] }}</ref>

9月8日，飞入风暴的[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机测得的[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]为每小时95公里，最低[[气压|气压]]1000[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，29.53[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）<ref name="prelim" />。气象部门起初预计达尼埃尔会进一步强化<ref name="ei">{{cite news | author = Jane Meinhardt | newspaper = The Evening Independent | date = 1986-09-08 | title = Tropical Storm Danielle is expected to slowly strengthen, turn northward | accessdate = 2016-05-22 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=cegLAAAAIBAJ&sjid=nVkDAAAAIBAJ&pg=3747,1789009&dq=danielle+tropical&hl=en | archive-date = 2022-01-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220114015700/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=cegLAAAAIBAJ&sjid=nVkDAAAAIBAJ&pg=3747%2C1789009&dq=danielle+tropical&hl=en }}</ref>，经过[[圣文森特和格林纳丁斯|圣文森特和格林纳丁斯]]期间，气旋中心北侧雨带中的风速已接近飓风标准，这片雨带便是从[[圣文森特岛|圣文森特岛]]上空掠过。在最高强度下保持约18小时后，行进至加勒比海东部的达尼埃尔开始因[[南美洲|南美洲]]北部的干燥空气侵入而弱化<ref name="prelim" /><ref>{{cite news | author = Verne Williams | newspaper = Miami Herald | date = 1986-09-10 | title = Danielle fizzles, is downgraded to a tropical wave}}</ref>。气旋沿南美大陆北海岸平行移动，环流和对流逐渐分离。9月9日晚，风暴降级成热带低气压，再于次日在加勒比地区西部完全消散<ref name="prelim" />。热带风暴埃尼埃尔是1986年间加勒比海仅有的热带气旋<ref name="HURDAT" />。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
风暴进入小安的列斯群岛海域前，当地收到[[小型船隻勸諭|小型船隻勸諭]]，随后巴巴多斯、圣文森特和格林纳丁斯也接获烈风警告<ref name="98upi">{{cite news | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | date = 1986-09-08 | newspaper = The Palm Beach Post | title = Storm Danielle Forms Off Barbados}}</ref>。面对气旋威胁，圣文森特岛上的学校、企业、商铺和主要民用机场被迫关闭<ref name="theday">{{cite news | author = Andrea Rowand | newspaper = The Day | date = 1986-09-10 | title = Danielle Loses Punch On Way to Caribbean | agency = Associated Press | accessdate = 2010-08-11 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=Be4gAAAAIBAJ&sjid=NnIFAAAAIBAJ&pg=2098,1847263&dq=danielle+tropical&hl=en | archive-date = 2022-01-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220114015648/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=Be4gAAAAIBAJ&sjid=NnIFAAAAIBAJ&pg=2098%2C1847263&dq=danielle+tropical&hl=en }}</ref>。更偏西侧的[[牙买加|牙买加]]也一度受到达尼埃尔的威胁，该国政府因此发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴观察预警]]<ref>{{cite news | author = Verne Williams | date = 1986-09-10 | title = Danielle's course prompts storm watch for Jamaica | newspaper = The Miami News}}</ref>。牙买加曾于两个月前因[[1986年大西洋飓风季#热带风暴安德鲁|热带风暴安德鲁]]的前身导致49人遇难，为避免悲剧重演，牙买加政府将两个小岛上的渔民转移，以防万一<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | agency = [[合众国际社|United Press International]] | newspaper = Mojave Daily Miner | title = Danielle weakens, loses storm status | accessdate = 2016-05-22 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=MBIPAAAAIBAJ&sjid=aIMDAAAAIBAJ&pg=3606,854895&dq=danielle+tropical&hl=en | archive-date = 2020-12-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201215140953/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=MBIPAAAAIBAJ&sjid=aIMDAAAAIBAJ&pg=3606%2C854895&dq=danielle+tropical&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

经过小安的列斯群岛期间，风暴的雨带直接袭击圣文森特岛并产生接近飓风强度的阵风。狂风导致岛上大面积停电，<ref name="prelim" />超过30套房屋的屋顶被毁<ref name="theday" />，该国的农作物也因狂风暴雨遭受重创<ref name="prelim" />。气旋过去12天后，圣文森特和格林纳丁斯又遭遇另一场强烈风暴袭击，两场风暴一共引起价值930万美元（1986年美元）的破坏，其中大部分是农作物受损。约有40%的香蕉作物不是被毁便是严重受创，无法继续栽培，另有8.3平方公里其它种类作物受严重影响。两场风暴一共致使120只动物死亡，但没有造成人命損失。除农作物受损外，两场风暴还造成上百套房屋被毁，共436套住宅受损，142人流离失所，只能暂时住进应急避难所。该国各地因暴雨引发多起[[泥石流|泥石流]]和洪灾，导致交通和公共服务网络受阻。<ref name="rw">{{cite news | author = [[联合国人道事务协调厅|United Nations Department of Humanitarian Affairs (DHA)]] | publisher = ReliefWeb | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151204213414/http://reliefweb.int/report/saint-vincent-and-grenadines/st-vincent-tropical-storm-danielle-sep-1986-undro-situation | accessdate = 2010-08-11 | date = 1986-10-06 | title = St. Vincent Tropical Storm Danielle Sep 1986 UNDRO Situation Reports 1–2 | archivedate = 2015-12-04 | deadurl = no | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/saint-vincent-and-grenadines/st-vincent-tropical-storm-danielle-sep-1986-undro-situation }}</ref>

巴巴多斯[[布里奇敦|布里奇敦]]的机场在达尼埃尔经过期间测得时速64公里阵风<ref name="ei" />。该国一艘海岸警卫队船只在格林纳丁斯南部的礁石上搁浅，所幸之后获救<ref name="prelim" /><ref name="theday" />。风暴雨带还掠过[[千里达及托巴哥|千里达及托巴哥]]，产生1.2米深的洪水，引发27起[[山崩|山体滑坡]]，还有四座桥梁被毁。该国遭受的破坏总额估计为800万[[特立尼达和多巴哥元|特立尼达和多巴哥元]]（相当于同年的120万美元）。<ref>{{cite web | author1 = C. B. Daniel | author2 = R. Maharaj | year = 1986 | title = Tropical Cyclones Affecting Trinidad and Tobago, 1725 to 2000 | publisher = Trinidad and Tobago Meteorological Service | accessdate = 2015-06-26 | archivedate = 2015-06-26 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150626132046/http://www.docstoc.com/docs/39273220/TROPICAL-CYCLONES-AFFECTING-TRINIDAD-AND-TOBAGO-1725-TO-2000 | url = http://www.docstoc.com/docs/39273220/TROPICAL-CYCLONES-AFFECTING-TRINIDAD-AND-TOBAGO-1725-TO-2000 }}</ref>

